author: stsp
msg: Fix memcached support for caches using svn_stringbuf_t values.
(memcache_get, memcache_set): Account for the svn_stringbuf_t invariant
s->data[s->len] == '\0' by copying the trailing NUL byte into the cache.
Fixes checksum mismatch errors seen during 'make check' with memcached.
